SUMMARY:Good Works
DESCRIPTION:Studio Montclair is proud to acknowledge the artist members who volunteer by providing an exhibition to highlight their artwork. While this exhibition by artist members is a tribute to their works\, their works on display are likewise a tribute to all people who donate their time and efforts to a greater good. \nSince its inception in 1997\, Studio Montclair has depended upon the work of volunteers. They are the backbone of the organization and it thrives only due to their tireless efforts on its behalf. Volunteers hang the works in the exhibitions\, paint the gallery after each show\, organize the receptions\, write press releases\, service the website\, maintain and post on social media\, and photograph our events. Volunteers serve on the Board of Trustees\, coordinate and facilitate the artist critique groups\, provide oversight on all matters pertaining to Art and the artist members\, and much more. \nParticipating Artists:\nNancy Blankenhorn\, Janet Boltax\, Phil Cantor\, Corrine Carr\, Dennis Connors\, Dan Epstein\, Peggy Gardner\, Linda Jacobs\, Amanda Kopp\, Steve Kushner\, Rick Ladd\, Paulina Olivares\, Denis Orloff\, Ted Papoulas\, Jim Price\, David Schlosser\, Paul Schmitz \nListing Information for the Exhibition: \nExhibition Dates: March 13 – April 10\, 2026\nOpening Reception: Friday\, March 13\, 6-8pm. All Are Welcome!\nGalleries: Studio Montclair’s Leach Gallery\, 641 Bloomfield Ave.\, Montclair\, NJ\nGallery Hours: Thursday – Sunday\, 1:00 – 5:00pm; please check SMI website for updates and additional hours\nStudio Montclair Contact Info: smi@studiomontclair.org\, 862-500-1447 \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/good-works/
LOCATION:Leach Gallery\, 641 Bloomfield Avenue\, Montclair\, 07042\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art & Culture
