SUMMARY:The Mills At Jersey Gardens Hosts Annual New Jersey Youth Symphony PLAYATHON
DESCRIPTION:The Mills at Jersey Gardens\, New Jersey’s largest outlet and value retail center\, is\nthrilled to host the annual Wharton Arts Day – a free afternoon of interactive musical activities and live\nperformances on Sunday\, March 22\, from 1:30–5:30 p.m. \nThe annual PLAYATHON fundraiser\, now a part of Wharton Arts Day\, supports music education\nprograms and scholarships that expand access to the performing arts for young people across the region. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
