SUMMARY:Intro to Tai Chi
DESCRIPTION:Experience the art of Tai Chi in this introductory session designed to connect mind and body through slow\, intentional movement. Guided by an experienced instructor\, you’ll flow through gentle sequences that build balance\, mobility\, and mental clarity while emphasizing breath and awareness. Open to all ages and fitness levels\, this practice offers a calming reset that supports posture\, focus\, and overall well-being. Leave feeling grounded\, refreshed\, and more connected to how you move and feel. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
