DESCRIPTION:Leave the stress at the door and kick back with a killer lineup of comics\, hosted in collaboration with Downtown Montclair. Whether you’re coming for date night\, friends night\, or just need a midweek reset — we’ve got the punchlines covered. \n🕖 Doors open at 7:00 PM\n🎬 Show starts at 7:30 PM\n🎟 $25 Tickets\n🍸 2-item minimum (cocktails\, mocktails\, or bites) \nTickets will be available at the door if we don’t sell out — but trust us\, you’ll want to grab yours early. \nBook now and let’s turn your night into a laugh-out-loud kind of vibe. \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
