SUMMARY:Ha! or Nah!: A Joke Lab!*TimeOut NY PICK!*
DESCRIPTION:Lauren LoGiudice brings here innovative comedy showcase to Newark! \nThis month’s show features: \nDanielle Slaughter (Good Vibes Comedy Festival)\nWayne Charles II (Comedy at Alke)Kofi Thomas (Amazon Prime)\nPat Bryne (WFMU)Dajon Alford (Nothin’ But Anthems)\nMatthew Silver (Idiot’s Hour) \nJoin our community of hilarious comedians (from HBO\, Netflix\, Comedy Central – and more!) for a night of heartwarming absurdity as they bring you their joke experiments in the most exciting new joke show from NYC… that’s also a Time Out New York pick! \nAudience members have said that it feels like a “communal experience” that’s “quirky and alive” and “if a tourist happens to find it they’re lucky.” \nHere are some other words from our audience members: \n“Good vibes. Good food. Good comedy.”\n“Witty\, creative\, and inclusive to everyone in a loving environment.”\n“Hilariously inappropriate\, yet kind.”\n“You get to go behind the curtain on how comedians make their work.” \n____ \nF.A.Q. \nCan I be one of the “first time comedians? Sure. Emailinthemidstprod@gmail.comand we’ll set you up. \nCan I come alone? Yes! Here’s what a recent audience member said about that: “Definitely a good atmosphere for a solo person\, everyone was very welcoming and friendly but also not overwhelming.” \nWhat kind of comedy is presented? Mostly standup\, as well as a character act or two. We include a diverse array of comedians experimenting with different ways to present standup. Audiences have loved this aspect of the show. Audience members have described it as: \n“Fun. Spontaneous.”\n“Unhinged….in the best way!”\n“Quirky and alive!”\n“Fun way to spend an evening: laugh and get dinner.” \nWill comedians make fun of me? This room is positive-vibes only! As one audience members said point blank: “You won’t be a target at this show.” \nHow can I stay in touch about future shows? Sign up for the producer’s email list at www.laurenlogiudice.com \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
URL:https://montclairlocal.news/event/ha-or-nah-a-joke-labtimeout-ny-pick/
LOCATION:NEWARK CULTURE CLU\, 563 Broad Street\, Newark\, 07102\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://montclairlocal.news/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/26-3-26-Ha-or-Nah-Jersey.jpg
END:VEVENT
